GeoTools
========

A few little methods to ease working with latitudes and longitudes.


Example
=======

class PassageReport < ActiveRecord::Base
  validates_latitude_of  :from_latitude,  :to_latitude
  validates_longitude_of :from_longitude, :to_longitude
end


